What you need to know:

Soya chairman Chris Mbaisi said they will not be rewarding top performers in area of sport, but rather recognizing efforts and possibilities during the last year.“Because sports are a resilient human endeavour, we shall host a sports symposium and a gala night to honour a few people who made an effort to overcome the diversity. The symposium will basically try to offer solutions to such situations where topics on mental health, sports fame/failure and investment, sports media and branding and doping will be tackled,” said Mbaisi.